Package: AquaWatch
Type: Package
Title: Client for the AquaWatch Water Quality Monitoring API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "James",
      family = "Dare",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "james.d@aquawatchsolutions.com",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2034-8421")
    )
Description: 
    Provides an R interface to the AquaWatch API for accessing water quality
    monitoring data from AquaWatch devices. The package supports
    authenticated requests, site discovery, and retrieval of time-filtered
    sample data using device Extended Unique Identifiers (EUIs). It is designed
    for reproducible environmental data analysis and integration into R-based
    workflows.
